<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ʿjbạ mkẖlṣy qd mạt mn ạ̉jly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā ʿajabaⁿạ mukẖalĩṣī
 qad̊ māta min̊ ạảj̊lī
 wasafaka ạldãma ạl̊karīm̊
 ʿan̊ kẖāṭīiⁿ̉ mitẖ̊lī

[V2]
 2- ạảyũ ḥabībiⁿ qad̊ samā
 mitẖ̊laka fī ạl̊ḥubĩ
 nazal̊ta min̊ ạảẘji ạlsãmā
 wamutã ʿan̊ dẖan̊bī

[V3]
 3- yā rabũ qad̊ ạảḥ̊bab̊tanī
 biḥubĩka ạl̊ʿajīb̊
 ḥubĩy ại̹zāʾa ḥubĩka
 lạa sẖaẙʾa yā ḥabīb̊

[V4]
 4- ại̹nĩy ạảsīru ḥubĩka
 mā dum̊tu fī ạl̊wujūd̊
 wakulũ qaṣ̊dī ạản̊ ạảray̱
 waj̊haka yā wadūd̊

[V5]
 5- fāản̊jizanã waʿ̊daka
 wafarĩḥi ạl̊qulūb̊
 wāản̊qidẖanã ʿab̊daka
 yā sayĩdī ạl̊maḥ̊būb̊

[V6]
 6- ạảḥabãnī mukẖalĩṣī
 naʿam̊ ạảḥabãnī
 yasūʿu qad̊ ạảḥabãnī
 lidẖā māta ʿanĩy</lyrics>
<aka>ạ̉ḥbny rby nʿm ạ̉ḥbny, ạ̉ḥbny mkẖlṣy nʿm ạ̉ḥbny</aka>
</song>